      "description": "Mark multiple notifications as read in a single request.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated tenant session/token (`auth:tenant-api`).\n\n**Request body:**\n- `ids` \u2014 required array of notification UUIDs (min: 1, max: 200, values must be distinct)\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Only updates notifications that belong to the authenticated user and are currently unread.\n- IDs that don't exist or belong to other users are silently ignored.\n- Returns the count of notifications actually updated."
